item.title: CVE-2023-50246|2023-12-13T20:43:50.862Z -- jqlang -- jq
item.description: jq is a command-line JSON processor. Version 1.7 is vulnerable to heap-based buffer overflow. Version 1.7.1 contains a patch for this issue.
